{"tid":679074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角行人專用區表演者指會轉到銅鑼灣演出","createTime":"2018-05-26T14:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T15:16:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b0d0a5244c5cdf2b3b8131f76d4644cee596e0","tid":679074,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】油尖旺區議會通過要求政府研究終止旺角行人專用區後，周末如常有人在專用區表演。有表演者指，會考慮轉到銅鑼灣等其他地方繼續演出；有市民則認為終止專用區會令旺角失去特色。<br />\n<br />\n這些歌聲、這些演出可能將會成為絕響。區議會通過研究終止行人專用區後的首個周末依然歌舞昇平。<br />\n<br />\n葉先生已擺檔6年，每逢周末這裏就是他開「個人演唱會」的場地，知道政府要研究終止這地方都覺得失望。<br />\n<br />\n周圍「快閃」的他們覺得處處都可以是他們的舞台。<br />\n<br />\n停下來欣賞的「知音人」都覺得可惜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307182&d=2iMymP5U%2FMYcNuHPv0fyLwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5a2d7ecb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307182&h=6f03382a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307182</a>"},{"pid":"b4edc1cc3b841598095f7bb9230c178ad6d42957","tid":679074,"uid":49697,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"好波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db7b278512b0755d7b9ac2dff33c94cc506c050","tid":679074,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"去港共總部"},{"pid":"93ce399ea1441f2ed1617e133728677dd090f830","tid":679074,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"去金鐘啦"},{"pid":"f06d68a36d3b59bb576194cebe71380bcc909539","tid":679074,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"去中環啦<img sr